{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as a sentient Vegetable who can transform into 6 different veggies with unique abilities. Escape the tormenting lab where you were created and are now being held captive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3401130/extras/store_banner_veggies_.png?t=1740393066\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>CARROT: </strong>Dash through the air and see in the dark using the carrot\u2019s abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>TOMATO:</strong> Fire your stem as a weaponized projectile to take out enemies in a blast. <strong>\u00a0</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>BROCCOLI: </strong>Swing through the air with the Broccoli\u2019s grappling hook ability.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>PEPPER: </strong>Traverse dangerous levels covered in acid much more safely with the near acid-proof pepper veggie.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>CUCUMBER: </strong>When you're as slim as a cucumber, you can fit through tight gaps and get to otherwise inaccessible spots.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>EGGPLANT: </strong>Break rocks and manipulate the environment through smashing stones and boulders to bits with the physically strongest veggie of them all!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3401130/extras/brocother_features_banner.png?t=1740393066\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Diverse terrain and environment\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Several boss fights\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">6 \u201chot-swappable\u201d veggies with different &amp; unique abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect DNA strands to unlock new abilities</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Unlock Broccoli","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3401130/b84cefb1df41cfa37d2a02371ccb507e2fa86f28.jpg"},{"name":"Unlock Carrot","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3401130/99880d0eef7ba191294ee0d817087d253bdd8275.jpg"},{"name":"Unlock Eggplant","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3401130/b2d90c33a7e65ad42bb495e7536c28cf405c55bc.jpg"},{"name":"Unlock Tomato","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3401130/43b5543690bd513971d8e33e67f859c9a6c65441.jpg"},{"name":"Beat The Demo!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3401130/397df95760dcf916bd7166fc3dbf5efaee4e967e.jpg"}],"total":5},"background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3401130?t=1740393066","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3401130?t=1740393066","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3401130/8731e727367f8e83377f72675009f1ede3f9cabb/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740393066","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3401130/8731e727367f8e83377f72675009f1ede3f9cabb/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740393066","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as a sentient Vegetable who can transform into 6 different veggies with unique abilities. Escape the tormenting lab where you were created and are 